<eesti>(2 (2)) T&auml;htp&auml;evaks tasumata maksusummalt v&otilde;i selle osalt, mis on v&otilde;rdne v&otilde;i v&auml;iksem Maksuameti ja tema kohalike asutuste poolt maksumaksjale tagastamisele kuuluvast enammakstud maksusummast, ei arvestata intresse: </eesti>
<inglise>(2 (2)) Interest is not calculated on an amount of tax or a part thereof unpaid by the due date which is equal to or less than the overpaid tax to be refunded to a taxpayer by the Tax Board and its local offices: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kui k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 10 1. l&otilde;ikes nimetatud taotlus esitati enne maksu tasumise t&auml;htp&auml;eva - maksusumma tasumise t&auml;htp&auml;evale j&auml;rgnevast p&auml;evast kuni enammakstud maksusumma tagastamise v&otilde;i maksumaksja muude rahaliste kohustustega tasaarvestamise p&auml;evani, viimane kaasa arvatud; </eesti>
<inglise>1) as of the date following the due date for payment of the amount of tax until the date of refund of the overpaid tax or the date of an offset of other financial obligations of the taxpayer, inclusive of the latter, if the application specified in subsection 10 (1) of this Act was filed prior to the due date of payment of the tax; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kui k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 10 1. l&otilde;ikes nimetatud taotlus esitati p&auml;rast maksu tasumise t&auml;htp&auml;eva - taotluse esitamisele j&auml;rgnevast p&auml;evast kuni enammakstud maksusumma tagastamise v&otilde;i maksumaksja muude rahaliste kohustustega tasaarvestamise p&auml;evani, viimane kaasa arvatud. </eesti>
<inglise>2) as of the date following the date on which the application was filed until the date of refund of the overpaid tax or the date of an offset of other financial obligations of the taxpayer, inclusive of the latter, if the application specified in subsection 10 (1) of this Act was filed after the due date for payment of the tax; </inglise>
