<eesti>Juriidilise isiku vastutus </eesti>
<inglise>Liability of legal persons </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Juriidilise isiku poolt: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) If a legal person: </inglise>
<eesti>1) maksuseaduses etten&auml;htud maksudeklaratsiooni t&auml;htp&auml;evaks esitamata j&auml;tmisel m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 5000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>1) fails to submit a tax return as prescribed in a tax Act by the due date, a fine of up to 5 000 kroons is imposed; </inglise>
<eesti>(10.04.96 j&otilde;ust.12.05.96 - RT I 1996, 29, 577) </eesti>
<inglise>(10.04.96 entered into force 12.05.96 - RT I 1996, 29, 577) </inglise>
<eesti>2) k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 11 (4) 7. l&otilde;ikes ja &sect; 12 1. l&otilde;ikes s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uete rikkumisel m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 10 000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>2) fails to comply with the requirements prescribed in subsections 11 (4) (7) and 12 (1) of this Act, a fine of up to 10 000 kroons is imposed; </inglise>
<eesti>(12.04.2000 j&otilde;ust.01.06.2000 - RT I 2000, 35, 216) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.04.2000 entered into force 01.06.2000 - RT I 2000, 35, 216) </inglise>
<eesti>3) takistuse tegemisel maksuhaldurile maksude tasumise &otilde;igsuse kontrollimisel, tasumisele kuuluva maksusumma m&auml;&auml;ramisel v&otilde;i maksuv&otilde;la sissen&otilde;udmisel ning maksuhalduri sellekohase ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmisel m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 20 000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>3) obstructs a tax authority during verification of the correctness of the payment of taxes, determination of the amount of tax to be paid or collection of tax arrears, or fails to perform a precept of a tax authority to this effect, a fine of up to 20 000 kroons is imposed; </inglise>
<eesti>(12.04.2000 j&otilde;ust.01.06.2000 - RT I 2000, 35, 216) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.04.2000 entered into force 01.06.2000 - RT I 2000, 35, 216) </inglise>
<eesti>4) maksuseaduses etten&auml;htust v&auml;iksema maksusumma v&otilde;i maksuseaduses etten&auml;htust suurema maksumaksjale tagastamisele kuuluva maksusumma n&auml;itamise eest maksudeklaratsioonis v&otilde;i muus maksuhaldurile esitatud dokumendis m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 40% summast, mille v&otilde;rra maksumaksja poolt n&auml;idatud maksusumma on v&auml;iksem maksuseaduse j&auml;rgi tasumisele kuuluvast maksusummast v&otilde;i maksumaksja poolt n&auml;idatud tagastamisele kuuluv maksusumma oli suurem maksuseaduse j&auml;rgi tagastamisele kuuluvast maksusummast; </eesti>
<inglise>4) indicates in a tax return or other document submitted to a tax authority a smaller amount of tax than prescribed in a tax Act or a greater amount of tax than that due to be refunded to the taxpayer pursuant to a tax Act, a fine is imposed in an amount of up to 40 per cent of the amount by which the amount of tax as indicated by the taxpayer is lower than the amount of tax to be paid pursuant to a tax Act or by which the amount of tax to be refunded as indicated by the taxpayer is greater than the amount of tax to be refunded pursuant to a tax Act; </inglise>
<eesti>(12.04.2000 j&otilde;ust.01.06.2000 - RT I 2000, 35, 216) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.04.2000 entered into force 01.06.2000 - RT I 2000, 35, 216) </inglise>
<eesti>5) punktis 4 nimetatud tegevuse eest, kui see pandi toime tahtlikult, m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 100% summast, mille v&otilde;rra maksumaksja poolt n&auml;idatud maksusumma on v&auml;iksem maksuseaduse j&auml;rgi tasumisele kuuluvast maksusummast v&otilde;i maksumaksja poolt n&auml;idatud tagastamisele kuuluv maksusumma oli suurem maksuseaduse j&auml;rgi tagastamisele kuuluvast maksusummast; </eesti>
<inglise>5) intentionally performs an activity specified in clause 4), a fine is imposed in an amount of up to 100 per cent of the amount by which the amount of tax as indicated by the taxpayer is lower than the amount of tax to be paid pursuant to a tax Act or by which the amount of tax to be refunded as indicated by the taxpayer is greater than the amount of tax to be refunded pursuant to a tax Act; </inglise>
<eesti>(12.04.2000 j&otilde;ust.01.06.2000 - RT I 2000, 35, 216) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.04.2000 entered into force 01.06.2000 - RT I 2000, 35, 216) </inglise>
