<eesti>8) kinnipidamisele kuuluva maksu kinni pidamata v&otilde;i &uuml;le kandmata j&auml;tmisel m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv summas, mis on v&otilde;rdne t&auml;htaegselt &uuml;lekandmata maksusummaga; </eesti>
<inglise>8) fails to withhold taxes or transfer taxes which have been withheld, a fine is imposed in an amount equal to the amount of tax not transferred during the prescribed term; </inglise>
<eesti>9) krediidiasutusele, kes ei t&auml;ida maksuhalduri poolt k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 24 1. l&otilde;ike punkti 1 alusel tehtud ettekirjutust v&otilde;i &sect; 25 4. l&otilde;ikes s&auml;testatud kohustust, m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv maksumaksja poolt t&auml;htajaks tasumata maksusumma ulatuses, kuid mitte &uuml;le maksumaksja pangakontol arestimise hetkel olnud summa; </eesti>
<inglise>9) who is a credit institution fails to comply with a precept issued by a tax authority on the basis of clause 24 (1) 1) of this Act or fails to perform the obligation provided for in subsection 25 (4) of this Act, a fine equal to the amount of tax unpaid by a taxpayer by the due date is imposed, whereupon the fine shall not exceed the amount in the bank account of the taxpayer at the moment of seizure of the bank account; </inglise>
