<inglise>(06.12.95 entered into force 01.02.96 - RT I 1995, 95, 1630) </inglise>
<eesti>11) ilma vastava maksustamisperioodi maksum&auml;rgita m&auml;ngulauaga hasartm&auml;ngu korraldamisel m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 100 000 krooni iga m&auml;ngukohas paikneva maksum&auml;rgita m&auml;ngulaua kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>11) organises gambling using a gambling table that does not have a revenue stamp for the corresponding taxable period, a fine of 50 000 kroons per gambling table without a revenue stamp in the gambling location is imposed; </inglise>
