<inglise>(06.12.95 entered into force 01.02.96 - RT I 1995, 95, 1630) </inglise>
<eesti>12) erim&auml;rgistatud k&uuml;tuse kasutamisel s&otilde;idukis mootorik&uuml;tusena m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 20 000 krooni iga s&otilde;iduki kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>12) uses fuel marked with a fiscal marker as motor fuel in a vehicle, a fine of 20 000 kroons per vehicle is imposed. </inglise>
<eesti>(23.09.97 j&otilde;ust.01.01.98 - RT I 1997, 73, 1201) </eesti>
<inglise>(23.09.97 entered into force 01.01.98 - RT I 1997, 73, 1201) </inglise>
<eesti>13) seaduses s&auml;testatud korras ja t&auml;htajaks maksuhalduri asutuses enda registreerimata j&auml;tmise eest m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 20 000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>13) fails to register with an office of a tax authority pursuant to the procedure and during the term provided by law, a fine of up to 20 000 kroons is imposed; </inglise>
<eesti>(12.04.2000 j&otilde;ust.01.06.2000 - RT I 2000, 35, 216) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.04.2000 entered into force 01.06.2000 - RT I 2000, 35, 216) </inglise>
<eesti>14) k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 18 alusel paigaldatud m&otilde;&otilde;turite v&otilde;i t&otilde;kendite rikkumise, k&otilde;rvaldamise v&otilde;i asendamise v&otilde;i muu tegevuse eest, mis ei v&otilde;imalda m&otilde;&otilde;turi v&otilde;i t&otilde;kendi otstarbekohast rakendamist, m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 20 000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>14) tampers with or removes or replaces a meter or preventive measure installed or implemented according to &sect; 18 of this Act, or carries out any other activity due to which a meter or preventive measure cannot be used as intended, a fine of up to 20 000 kroons is imposed; </inglise>
<eesti>(12.04.2000 j&otilde;ust.01.06.2000 - RT I 2000, 35, 216) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.04.2000 entered into force 01.06.2000 - RT I 2000, 35, 216) </inglise>
<eesti>15) tulumaksuseaduse (RT I 1999, 101, 903; RT I 2001, 11, 49; 16, 69; 50, 283; 59, 359) &sect; 40 6. l&otilde;ikes etten&auml;htud t&otilde;endi maksumaksjale v&auml;ljastamata j&auml;tmise eest m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 5000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>15) fails to issue a certificate prescribed in subsection 40 (6) of the Income Tax Act (RT I 1999, 101, 903; RT I 2001, 11, 49; 16, 69; 50, 283; 59, 359) to a taxpayer, a fine of up to 5000 kroons is imposed; </inglise>
