<eesti>18 (1)) sigarettide v&otilde;&otilde;randamise eest nende m&uuml;&uuml;gipakendile kinnitatud maksum&auml;rgile tr&uuml;kitud hinnast k&otilde;rgema hinnaga - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 5000 kuni 40 000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>18 (1)) transfers cigarettes at a price which is higher than the price printed on the revenue stamp attached to the sales packaging of the cigarettes, a fine of between 5000 and 40 000 kroons is imposed; </inglise>
