<inglise>19) fails to re-register a lorry pursuant to the requirements arising from Heavy Goods Vehicle Tax Act (RT I 2000, 81, 515) or uses a heavy goods vehicle the registration certificate of which is not re-registered, a fine of up to 20 000 kroons is imposed on the owner or possessor of the lorry. </inglise>
