<eesti>(1 (1)) Juriidilise isiku poolt maksuseaduse rikkumise kohta koostatakse vastavalt haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustiku paragrahvis 229 s&auml;testatule protokoll, mis esitatakse hiljemalt kolme t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul ametiisikule, kes on volitatud arutama juriidilise isiku poolt maksuseaduse rikkumise asja. </eesti>
<inglise>(1 (1)) A report on a violation of a tax Act by a legal person shall be prepared pursuant to the provisions of &sect; 229 of the Code of Administrative Offences and submitted not later than within three working days to an official authorised to hear matters concerning violations of tax Acts by legal persons. </inglise>
