<eesti>(2) Juriidilise isiku poolt maksuseaduse rikkumise asja arutamise ja karistuse m&auml;&auml;ramise &otilde;igus on maksuhalduri peadirektoril, tema aset&auml;itjal, maksuhalduri kohaliku asutuse direktoril ja nende poolt volitatud isikutel. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Upon violation by a legal person of a tax Act, the director general of a tax authority, his or her deputy, the director of a local office of a tax authority and persons authorised by them have the right to hear the matter and to impose punishment. </inglise>
<eesti>Kohalike maksude seaduse rikkumise asja arutamise ja karistuse m&auml;&auml;ramise &otilde;igus on volikogu poolt volitatud ametnikul. </eesti>
<inglise>An official authorised by the council has the right to hear a matter concerning violation of the Local Taxes Act and to impose punishment. </inglise>
